name: DevFest Southern Africa 2018
description:
GDG DevFest 2018 is our annual all-day developer conference that offers speaker sessions across multiple product areas, codelabs, hackathon and more! After a successful GDG Southern Africa 2017 in Harare, Zimbabwe, we wanted to bring back the fire, this time in Gaborone, Botswana. GDG Gaborone in collaboration with GDG Windhoek.
We are expecting developers, designers and entrepreneurs from all over Southern Africa, along with some Googlers and Google Developer experts in the area.

1. Mobile ( Kotlin & Flutter)
2. Web
3. Machine Learning
4. IoT ( Android Things)
5. Cloud (Firebase & GCP)

On the night of the 9th of November we plan to host the Women Techmakers welcome cocktail to build momentum for women participation throughout the Devfest
